      "description": "NP0032_MiniEvent_FindTreasure_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "順調ね、続けましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/3afX95p129cz4VwXFuZpW9Hh86COggv1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEvent_FindTreasure_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "いい傾向ね、悪くないわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/sOpZ33Hs719z9tRHheyYD01eibVoB2jQ.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventBoxshop_SPBuy_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "なるほど。良いものを当てたわね。おめでとう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/ByKWkugrwNe50MBKEmZSnAGbOiuluOb3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventBoxshop_SPBuy_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ああ、これは良い商品よ。私が保証するわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/Bz0Y65W7REaUDTa5pj0Hy5zB8vqymocf.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventBoxshop_SPBuy_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "おめでとう。やはり先生は幸運の持ち主なのね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/onz4OAtsitQkgGDbjlwGnwCdAbzJRrn6.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventCardpickup_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "まさか当てるだなんて......すごいわね、先生！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/sKLPqAvf9uzLAZeSHmeKsskQbqOEaEvb.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventCardpickup_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "悪くないわね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/GCQoUxflPmERW0TmHRbCFsnnz45UW2UR.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventCardpickup_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "良いと思うわ。  ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/Z7VZ8W9ubOgJQUtQKU6IH2AFbCJk9G09.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventCardpickup_4",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "まだまだあるもの。続けていきましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/xr4AzscCjCONADqsdaSYhpmpHE28cHb9.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLobby_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "あら、何かあったのかしら？ 困っている事があるのなら、なんでも相談してちょうだい。 私は、先生の補佐としてここにいるのだから。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/GuNPDYvuRnZI9jiLA2NP2qVjZtT6IyZr.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLobby_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "そう警戒しないでちょうだい。 …私も傷つくのよ？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/E4iBjpzuAW87oH30G6CcAJBgx37KKsdU.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLobby_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "あの…私の事はいいから、 あっちを確認してちょうだい。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/C2ow8HSJes9ocOED99w06QcNOv2DUqyR.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLobby_4",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "だから、私の事はいいから…",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/qvG7H7vAMlhCZtsxAHozNnNNx7ixSk86.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLobby_5",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "少し集中してもらえるかしら？ いえ、私ではなく、仕事に…。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/C0z4dOyU7iAFBRU6dmlFWFsE5lan2CNE.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLogin_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "待っていたわ、先生。時間を無駄にはできないの。 さあ、早速はじめましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/QHGxehkCeznMTPvMiIUXzPVCdIH3pGWO.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLogin_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "これが本日の業務内容。先生の活躍、期待しているわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/4rxqdkPz1rRUZgHfMK3HhgVNGLMH3kIr.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLogin_Season_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "まだ事態は終わっていないわ。 気を引き締めていきましょう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/H5padTkR1zQb5yt2LK2HIpKjeif89fg7.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLogin_Season_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "終わりが見えてきたわね。 最後まで、向上心を忘れないように。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/VcpCelDzOjBNnB2YZkQd8VBI4T9cVnYr.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventLogin_Season_End",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "無事終了したわね。 やり残しがないか、今のうちに確認してちょうだい。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/pKz3LWguy9h4KNKkSMjJpqP6XI7mPW7r.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventMission_Day_End",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "本日の業務はこれですべてね。お疲れ様、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/HG8YATxz4nTXY7H7jSUkVtpqeoNpHR3Y.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventMission_Get_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "はい、お疲れ様、先生。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/Gm4lHOCYQJFnm3F9U7rpQth69aXG9alU.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventMission_Get_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "これで解決ね。ありがとう。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/kn725efR0zAEcshbxqeWjVlwVlJVoBu2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventShop_Buy_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "それを選んだの。なるほど。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/TDgrfbX4nJFGrJAi6Vf0y67wOuAiLzBb.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventShop_Buy_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "ふむ…私も異論はないわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/Y6M1cJjlXr9CzLtJurBtzcQJB4lQ6JyP.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventShop_Buy_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "そう、良い判断だと思うわ。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/SfUYC3FUzoARUwDlB6DcGUz3b7njC7ej.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventShop_Buy_4",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "先生にとって、それが必要なのね。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/3mbTMDrKwMIu6labUAr70H4AFYAHaLJF.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "NP0032_MiniEventShop_End",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "おかげで助かったわ、先生。 次回もまた、お願いしてもいいかしら？",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/df54TpV6iHz03ScdvXt8vNaC3gxawufy.ogg"
    }
  ],
  "voice_cn": [
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventboxshop_spbuy_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "原来如此， 您抽到了好东西呢，恭喜。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventboxshop_spbuy_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventboxshop_spbuy_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "啊啊，这个东西很棒呢， 我可以保证。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventboxshop_spbuy_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventboxshop_spbuy_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "恭喜， 老师运气果然很好呢。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventboxshop_spbuy_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventcardpickup_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "不会抽到了那个东西吧…… 老师好厉害。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventcardpickup_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventcardpickup_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "唔，还不坏嘛。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventcardpickup_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventcardpickup_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "也还不错嘛？",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventcardpickup_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventcardpickup_4",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "其他的还有剩，继续吧。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventcardpickup_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlobby_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "嗯，您遇到了什么问题吗？因为我是老师的助手，所以遇到困难的话， 请尽管和我说。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlobby_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlobby_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "不要这么生分嘛。……我也是会受伤的哦？",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlobby_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlobby_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "嗯……不用担心我，先去确认一下那边吧，",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlobby_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlobby_4",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "都说了不用担心我了……",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlobby_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlobby_5",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "能不能专心一点？不，不是说对我， 是对工作……",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlobby_5.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlogin_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "老师，我等您很久了。那事不宜迟， 我们马上开始吧？",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlogin_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlogin_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "这是今天的工作内容， 期待您的表现。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlogin_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlogin_season_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "一切还没结束，打起精神继续前进吧。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlogin_season_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlogin_season_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "终点就在眼前。但直到结束之前， 都请保持上进心。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlogin_season_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventlogin_season_end",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "顺利结束了。请检查一下 是否有剩余的工作吧。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventlogin_season_end.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventmission_day_end",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "今天的工作就到此结束了。  辛苦了。老师。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventmission_day_end.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventmission_get_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "嗯，老师您辛苦了。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventmission_get_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventmission_get_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "这个也解决了呢，谢谢。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventmission_get_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventshop_buy_1",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "选择了那个吗？ 原来如此。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventshop_buy_1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventshop_buy_2",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "嗯，好的， 我也没有异议。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventshop_buy_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventshop_buy_3",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "原来如此， 我认为这个决定很棒。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventshop_buy_3.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventshop_buy_4",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "原来老师需要这个啊。",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventshop_buy_4.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "np0032_minieventshop_end",
      "category": "other",
      "text": "谢谢您帮助我，老师。下次也可以请您帮忙吗？",
      "text_original": "",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E6%89%87%E5%96%9C%20%E8%91%B5/original/cn/np0032_minieventshop_end.ogg"
    }
  ],
